    <title>Hexo博客</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/05/14/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/05/14/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</id>
    <published>2019-05-14T07:28:19.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-14T08:39:07.872Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装-node"><a href="#安装-node" class="headerlink" title="安装 node"></a>安装 node</h2><blockquote><p>官网下载，安装，同时会自动下载npm包管理工具</p></blockquote><p>输入node -v检查是否安装完成。</p><h2 id="下载hexo"><a href="#下载hexo" class="headerlink" title="下载hexo"></a>下载hexo</h2><blockquote><p>npm 国内直接下载hexo速度感人。建议配置国内淘宝源。</p></blockquote><h3 id="配置taobao源"><a href="#配置taobao源" class="headerlink" title="配置taobao源"></a>配置taobao源</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class="line">npm config get registry  //返回https://registry.npm.taobao.org，说明镜像配置成功。</span><br><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="下载hexo-1"><a href="#下载hexo-1" class="headerlink" title="下载hexo"></a>下载hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置Hexo"><a href="#配置Hexo" class="headerlink" title="配置Hexo"></a>配置Hexo</h2><blockquote><p>新建一个目录，命名HexoBlog（随意）。进入这个目录。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>初始化完后，可以运行hexo s 检查下。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 浏览器地址栏输入 localhost：4000 可以看到hexo的第一篇博客。</p><h2 id="Helloword"><a href="#Helloword" class="headerlink" title="Helloword"></a>Helloword</h2><p>进入博客文件夹，在终端运行hexo n “”创建第一篇。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n <span class="string">"HelloWorldForHexo"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts/</span><br><span class="line">vi HelloWorldForHexo.md <span class="comment"># 利用vi编辑md，也可以在其他markdown软件编辑。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ../.. <span class="comment"># 回到博客文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean </span><br><span class="line">hexo g <span class="comment"># 生成</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s <span class="comment"># 到localhost:4000预览</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装Git-部署插件"><a href="#安装Git-部署插件" class="headerlink" title="安装Git 部署插件"></a>安装Git 部署插件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成后，需要修改_config.yml文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在文件的最下面修改成</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/demo/demo.github.io.git <span class="comment"># 你自己的GitHub仓库地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  branch: master <span class="comment"># 分支</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d <span class="comment"># 部署到github上</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
